Class Student

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3.Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Student>
Direct Known Subclasses:
NonResident, Resident
public abstract class Student extends Object implements Comparable<Student>
Creates Student objects utilizing user input. Student class is abstract If input is valid, student information from TuitionManagerView.fxml is utilized to create a Student object.
Author:
Sharukh Khan, Hamad Naveed
